* Andrew McCracken <U+2013> bass guitar (2004&ndash;2006)
* Joel Bath <U+2013> drums, percussion (2004&ndash;2005)

==Nominations==
In 2009, the band was nominated for a [[2009 Juno Awards|Juno Award]] for New Group of the Year along with [[The Stills]] (who won the award), [[Beast (Canadian band)|Beast]], [[Crystal Castles (band)|Crystal Castles]], and [[Plants and Animals]]. Cancer Bats were also nominated in the "Rock Album of the Year" category at the 2011 Juno Awards.

